{"tid":592333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"性侵16歲男學生　日籍寄宿媽媽被逮捕","createTime":"2018-03-14T06:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T09:41:33.000Z","uid":34498,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"f53a7922fa8c5615586f37a6b51980e915c84092","tid":592333,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"日本一名男學生到夏威夷當交換生，竟慘遭寄宿家庭女主人性侵。當地媒體報導，36歲的清水里加（Rika Shimizu）被指控7項性侵罪名遭送法辦。受害者是一名16歲來自日本的交換學生，他向警方表示，從去年10月至今年2月，遭「寄宿媽媽」清水里加性侵至少10次。少年陳述，他去年10月頭部受傷無法自行下床如廁或更換衣物，均需仰賴清水幫忙。某夜，清水進入少年房間，首次性侵他。少年說他不斷請求清水停止性侵，卻被清水威脅，若他反抗或說出此事，她將反控他強暴。清水更威脅要讓少年遭退學並結束交換學生計畫。<br />\n<br />\n清水在夏威夷經營寄宿家庭，專門接待從日本來的交換學生。少年律師痛批，清水把自己塑造成「寄宿媽媽」的溫馨形象，承諾給予被害人學習英語的健康安全環境，卻對未成年人下此毒手。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180314/1314367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180314%2F1314367&d=IXf6xLPnSzXebfTauHxT6QdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=fd14d4b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180314%2F1314367&h=1928177f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180314/1314367</a>"},{"pid":"742296913226eff7e8b09c3915be4a206a1ed1ef","tid":592333,"uid":22566,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07954481424558b8e911d9a77212e41b1aa3046","tid":592333,"uid":38293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"cdc6dc9eac2052fb71d82759dafa9497e6058c73","tid":592333,"uid":51092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">快</span>"},{"pid":"4a512b1ad978b9568512a1ce355d165c9262d731","tid":592333,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:32:08.000Z","msg":"36歲都唔係好老姐<im